## Step 2 — Create Package Type Custom Record

1. **Customization > Lists, Records & Fields > Record Types > New**
   - Name: `Package Type`
   - ID: `_lime_package_type` (NetSuite will prefix with `customrecord`, giving `customrecord_lime_package_type`)
   - Allow Inline Editing: Yes
   - Save

2. **Add fields** (on the record type's Fields subtab):

   | Field Label      | ID (no prefix)         | Type    | Required |
   |-----------------|------------------------|---------|----------|
   | Default Length  | `_lime_pt_length`      | Decimal | No       |
   | Default Width   | `_lime_pt_width`       | Decimal | No       |
   | Default Height  | `_lime_pt_height`      | Decimal | No       |
   | Dimension Unit  | `_lime_pt_dim_unit`    | List/Record → `custlist_lime_pack_dim_unit` | No |

3. **Create the four Package Type records:**
   Navigate to the Package Type list (via the custom record list or direct URL) and create:
   - EU Pallet (enter standard EU pallet dimensions: 120 × 80 × 144 cm or as applicable)
   - US Pallet (enter standard US pallet dimensions: 48 × 40 × 57 in or as applicable)
   - Carton (leave defaults blank; users enter per-carton dimensions each time)
   - Other (leave defaults blank)

