## Step 3 — Create Ship Unit Custom Record

One record per pallet/box created during a packing session.

1. **Customization > Lists, Records & Fields > Record Types > New**
   - Name: `Ship Unit`
   - ID: `_lime_ship_unit`
   - Allow Inline Editing: Yes
   - Save

2. **Add fields:**

   | Field Label        | ID (no prefix)           | Type                                              | Required |
   |--------------------|--------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|----------|
   | Transfer Orders    | `_lime_ship_unit_orders` | Multiple Select → Transaction                     | No       |
   | Item Fulfillments  | `_lime_ship_unit_fulfill`| Multiple Select → Transaction                     | No       |
   | Package Type       | `_lime_ship_unit_pt`     | List/Record → Package Type                        | No       |
   | Weight Unit        | `_lime_ship_unit_wu`     | List/Record → `custlist_lime_pack_weight_unit`    | No       |
   | Dimension Unit     | `_lime_ship_unit_du`     | List/Record → `custlist_lime_pack_dim_unit`       | No       |
   | Length             | `_lime_ship_unit_length` | Decimal                                           | No       |
   | Width              | `_lime_ship_unit_width`  | Decimal                                           | No       |
   | Height             | `_lime_ship_unit_height` | Decimal                                           | No       |
   | Weight             | `_lime_ship_unit_weight` | Decimal                                           | No       |
   | Packing Notes        | `_lime_ship_unit_note`     | Long Text                                              | No       |
   | Unpacked             | `_lime_ship_unit_status`   | Checkbox (default: unchecked)                          | No       |
   | Shipment Summary     | `_lime_ship_unit_summ`     | List/Record → Shipment Summary                         | No       |
   | Ship Unit Volume     | `_lime_ship_unit_vol`      | Decimal — auto-calculated as L × W × H                | No       |
   | Ship Unit Volume Unit| `_lime_ship_unit_vol_unit` | List/Record → `customlist_lime_volume_units`           | No       |

   > **Shipment Summary** must be created (Step 4) before this field can reference it.
   > Create the Ship Unit record type first, add all other fields, then return to add
   > the Shipment Summary field after Step 4 is complete.

