## Step 4 — Create Shipment Summary Record

One record per packing session. Groups all Ship Units and carries session-level metadata.

1. **Customization > Lists, Records & Fields > Record Types > New**
   - Name: `Shipment Summary`
   - ID: `_lime_shipment_summary`
   - Allow Inline Editing: Yes
   - Save

2. **Add fields:**

   | Field Label            | ID (no prefix)                | Type                                           | Required |
   |------------------------|-------------------------------|------------------------------------------------|----------|
   | Packing Notes          | `_lime_ss_notes`              | Long Text                                      | No       |
   | Total Packages         | `_lime_ss_pkg_count`          | Integer                                        | No       |
   | Aggregate Weight       | `_lime_ss_weight`             | Decimal                                        | No       |
   | Weight Unit            | `_lime_ss_wu`                 | List/Record → `custlist_lime_pack_weight_unit` | No       |
   | Packed By              | `_lime_ss_packed_by`          | List/Record → Employee                         | No       |
   | Packed Date            | `_lime_ss_date`               | Date/Time with Timezone                        | No       |
   | Location               | `_lime_ss_location`           | List/Record → Location                         | No       |
   | Delivery Location      | `_lime_ss_deliv_location`     | List/Record → Location                         | No       |
   | Ship Summary Orders    | `_lime_ss_orders`             | Multiple Select → Transaction                  | No       |
   | Ship Summary Fulfillments | `_lime_ss_fulfillments`    | Multiple Select → Transaction                  | No       |
   | Inventory Status       | `_lime_ss_inventory_status`   | List/Record → Inventory Status                 | No       |
   | Shipment Sent to OTM?  | *(add as needed)*             | Checkbox (default: unchecked)                  | No       |
   | Unpacked               | `_lime_ss_unpacked`           | Checkbox (default: unchecked)                              | No       |
   | Unpacked Date          | `_lime_ss_unpack_date`        | Date/Time with Timezone                                    | No       |
   | Shipment Summary       | `_lime_ss_summary`            | Long Text                                                  | No       |
   | Aggregate Volume       | `_lime_ss_volume`             | Decimal — sum of all Ship Unit volumes for this session    | No       |
   | Volume Unit            | `_lime_ss_vol_unit`           | List/Record → `customlist_lime_volume_units`               | No       |

   > **Location** (`_lime_ss_location`) is auto-stamped as the Item Fulfillment's "Ship From" location (not the logged-in user's default location).
   >
   > **Delivery Location** (`_lime_ss_deliv_location`) is auto-stamped as the Transfer Order's "Transfer To" location.
   >
   > **Ship Summary Orders** and **Ship Summary Fulfillments** are auto-populated with all Transfer Orders and Item Fulfillments included in the packing session.
   >
   > **Inventory Status** (`_lime_ss_inventory_status`) is auto-stamped from the first inventory assignment found across the fulfillment lines. If no inventory detail exists on any line (e.g. non-tracked items), the field is left blank.
   >
   > **Shipment Sent to OTM?** is a manual checkbox — not populated by the suitelet or scripts.
   >
   > **Shipment Summary** (field `_lime_ss_summary`) is auto-generated on submission.
   > Format: `Pallet #1: 48 x 40 x 66 - 846 lbs //Pallet #2: 48 x 40 x 76 - 456 lbs //`
   >
   > **Record Name** is auto-generated from the IF transaction numbers joined with dashes (e.g. `IF-1001-IF-1002`).
   >
   > **Aggregate Volume** (`_lime_ss_volume`) is auto-calculated as the sum of L × W × H across all Ship Units in the session.
   >
   > **Volume Unit** (`_lime_ss_vol_unit`) is auto-set based on the Dimension Unit of the packages: `CM` → `CU M`; `IN` → `CU F`.

3. **Return to Ship Unit (Step 3)** and add the Shipment Summary field now that the record type exists.

