## Step 6 — Create Center Category (Navigation Links)

This step adds Pack Orders and Unpack Orders links to the **Transactions** tab of the Classic Center, allowing warehouse staff to access the suitelets directly without opening an order first.

1. Navigate to **Customization > Centers and Tabs > Center Categories > New**

2. Fill in the following:

   | Field        | Value                               |
   |--------------|-------------------------------------|
   | Label        | `Pack Orders`                       |
   | ID           | `custcentercategory_lime_pack_orders` |
   | Center Type  | `Classic Center`                    |
   | Center Tab   | `Transactions`                      |

3. On the **Links** subtab, add two rows:

   | Link                    | Label           |
   |-------------------------|-----------------|
   | Lime SL Pack Orders     | `Pack Orders`   |
   | Lime SL Unpack Orders   | `Unpack Orders` |

   > "Lime SL Pack Orders" and "Lime SL Unpack Orders" refer to the deployed Suitelet scripts (`customscript_lime_sl_pack_fulfill` and `customscript_lime_sl_unpack_fulfill`). They will appear in the link picker once the Suitelet deployments from Step 6 are in **Released** status.

4. Click **Save**.

After saving, users with access to the Transactions tab will see a **Pack Orders** section with both links. Clicking either link opens the respective suitelet directly (no order context required).

