## Script Execution Logs

All scripts log to **System > Monitoring > Script Execution Logs**.

| Script                                | What to look for                                             |
|---------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| `customscript_lime_rl_pack_fulfill`   | getPickedFulfillments, getDropdownData, submitPacking        |
| `customscript_lime_rl_unpack_fulfill` | Unpack operations, IF reverts, summary flag                  |
| `customscript_lime_ue_if_pack_btns`   | Button injection errors, createdfrom type lookup             |

Change log level to `Error` in production deployments to reduce noise.

